orts as chief strategy officer during the company’s prominent growth era acquiring over  companies in less than five years he then became svp of the routing and service provider technology group where he managed over  engineers in early  this was an  billion business for cisco he was considered the righthand man and successor of ceo john chambers in  he left cisco and became eir at sequoia capital a few months later he was appointed ceo of joost in  he became general partner at index ventures contents  early life  cisco  index ventures  boards  personal life  awards  references early lifeedit volpi was born in milan italy when he was five his family moved to tokyo japan where he lived until he moved to the united states in  he earned a bs in mechanical engineering  and an ms in manufacturing systems engineering  from stanford university and an mba from the stanford graduate school of business  volpi began his career at hewlett packards optoelectronics division in  where he was both in engineering and in marketing while at hp he met his future wife toni c cupal he returned to stanford for an mba from the graduate school of business  ciscoedit volpi joined cisco systems in  in the nascent business development group he was promoted to leading acquisitions at cisco starting in april  as chief strategy officer for the company he led corporate strategy business development and strategic alliances during his tenure he and his team were responsible for the acquisition of over  companies in  years including a nearly b acquisition of scientific atlanta their acquisition strategy is widely regarded as a model for tech mergers and acquisitions in  he was named to the mit technology review tr as one of the top  innovators in the world under the age of  he was promoted to the chief strategy office working for ceo john chambers until  some press speculated he was heir apparent to chambers moving into an operational role as a senior vice president and general manager he led the routing and switching teams then coled the routing and service provider group with prem jain until  during this time ciscos first carrier routing system product was announced the crs in  from  until  volpi was ceo of joost an internet startup focused on online tv which was founded by skype founders niklas zennstrom and janus friis in september  a lawsuit was filed against volpi by skype’s founders in conjunction with the proposed divestiture of skype from ebay the lawsuit was dropped in november  index venturesedit at index ventures volpi invests in earlystage companies across the internet telecom networking and media sectors he currently sits on the boards of lookout path soundcloud big switch networks centrify hortonworks zuora elasticsearch fuzebox and pure storage volpi also contributes to the firm’s late stage growth fund through his investment in sonos boardsedit volpi is an independent director of exor company and was a board member of swedish mobile giant ericsson between  and  in addition he previously served on the boards of opsware now hp tibco skype storsimple cloudcom and clearwire volpi currently serves on the board of witness a nonprofit organization which uses video to open the eyes of the world to human rights violations he previously served on the advisory council for the stanford university graduate school of business personal lifeedit volpi is trilingual and married with  children his father is vittorio volpi an executive at the united bank of switzerland awardsedit network world  power issue –  most powerful people in networking  forbes midas list   worlds smartest tech investors referencesedit  a b andy reinhardt august   michaelangelo volpi vicepresident business development cisco systems business week retrieved june     a b mike volpi linkedin profile retrieved june     a b mike volpi nndbcom  mike volpi  crunchbase profile  can mike volpi make cisco sizzle again  businessweek   young innovators under  technology review  retrieved august     kar